    "text": "Public Assistance Sought to Apprehend Wanted Suspect The Western Province South Crime Investigation Division is conducting investigations to apprehend suspects in connection with a murder committed by two unidentified individuals who arrived on a motorcycle at a shop located in the Papiliyana Road area of Nedimala within the Dehiwala Police Division on 19.05.2025. Police are requesting public assistance to locate and arrest the individual who is believed to have been the motorcycle rider involved in this offence. The suspect\u2019s details are as follows: Suspect Details Name: Senaratne Dhananjaya Kaushalya Perera Address: No. 41/14, Oban Place, Dehiwala A photograph of the suspect is being circulated to the media. Members of the public who possess any information regarding his whereabouts are kindly requested to contact the following telephone numbers immediately: Contact Numbers: \u2022 Officer-in-Charge / Western Province South Crime Investigation Division \u2013 071 8596065 \u2022 Western Province South Crime Investigation Division \u2013 011 2809077 The police kindly request media institutions to widely publicize this notice for the information and assistance of the public. Police Media",
